cdata.name: Cryptonetix
cdata.desc:
Cryptonetix is a platform that presents daily news and analysis related to cryptocurrencies. Users can access tools which assist them in trading digital assets as well as to be updated about the crypto financial world. Cryptonetix was designed for asset education, management, analytics, and funding for rapid expanding cryptocurrency markets.

The CIX token is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is a utility token and can be applied to access features and services available within Cryptonetix.
